ulence, especially for stars with projected rotation speed\n$v\\sin{i_{\\star}} \\lesssim 5$ km/s. This reinforces earlier claims, and the\nstellar inclination estimated from the combination of measurements from\nspectroscopy and photometric variation for slowly rotating stars needs to be\ninterpreted with caution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 May 2018 04:36:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-06"}
