isition function produces more accurate posterior approximations, as\ncompared to common strategies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 May 2018 11:34:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Sep 2018 16:13:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-14"}
