 and to leading-order in the cubic and\nquartic in spin interactions. The radiation reaction dynamics is presented\nexplicitly through the third-and-half post-Newtonian order for spinless\nobjects, and, for spinning bodies, to leading-order in the spin-orbit and\nspin1-spin2 couplings. The most important historical issues get pointed out.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 May 2018 14:34:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Sep 2018 13:58:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 20 May 2019 16:25:15 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 7 Jan 2020 12:42:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
